8. git show: git show will display the detailed information about the commit.
   command: git show commit_id

[root@ip-172-31-8-220 devops-repo]# git show 22f27c87b449ba6cf9404c5c101c39af3566bf28
commit 22f27c87b449ba6cf9404c5c101c39af3566bf28 (HEAD -> master)
Author: GoudSagar <goud.sagar.t@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 4 02:04:21 2025 +0000

    Adding file.txt

